[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA libFuzzer session running `PDFExtractTextFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput` terminated [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith a timeout after approximately [0m[1;36m27.8[0m[39m seconds. The main application thread was [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbusy inside the Apache PDFBox Type1 font parsing routine [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`Type1Parser.parseBinary`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m when the timeout occurred. No explicit crash or [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexception is reported—only a prolonged execution leading to a fuzzer timeout.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Issue  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  During fuzz testing of PDF text extraction, the fuzzer exited with an “ERROR: [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibFuzzer: timeout” after roughly [0m[1;36m27.84[0m[39m seconds of elapsed time. The thread dump [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mshows the main thread in a RUNNABLE state, consuming CPU time in the native [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcallback `traceConstCmpInt`, invoked from `Type1Parser.parseBinary`.  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Vulnerability Type  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  This behavior corresponds to a performance or availability issue [0m[1;39m([0m[39mhang/timeout[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39makin to a denial-of-service condition, rather than a memory safety or logic error.[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Observations and Findings  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The fuzzer entry point is `PDFExtractTextFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput`, which [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcalls PDFBox’s `PDFTextStripper.getText`.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Execution flows through PDFBox font-loading and text-stream processing:  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    – `PDFontFactory.createFont` → `PDType1Font.<init>` → `Type1Font.createWithPFB`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m→ `Type1Parser.parse` → `Type1Parser.parseBinary`.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The hotspot in the stack trace is `traceConstCmpInt` [0m[1;39m([0m[39ma Jazzer runtime native [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcallback[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, indicating heavy instrumentation overhead or repeated comparisons during[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbinary parsing.  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • No other threads appear to be blocked on locks; the JVM’s housekeeping threads [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mGC, finalizer, reference handler, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are idle or waiting normally.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Areas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. **Type1Parser.parseBinary** [0m[1;39m([0m[39morg.apache.fontbox.type1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Analyze loops or [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecursive structures in the PFB/Type1 font binary parser that may run unbounded or [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtake excessive time on certain inputs.  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. **TraceDataFlowNativeCallbacks.traceConstCmpInt** [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mcom.code_intelligence.jazzer.runtime[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Assess whether the instrumentation callback[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis causing undue overhead in tight parsing loops.  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. **PDType1Font and PDFontFactory** [0m[1;39m([0m[39morg.apache.pdfbox.pdmodel.font[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Review the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfont creation pipeline to see how binary data is fed into the parser and whether [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpre-validation or size checks might limit pathological cases.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. **PDFTextStripper/PDFStreamEngine** [0m[1;39m([0m[39morg.apache.pdfbox.text and [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontentstream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Although the hang is in Type1 parsing, inspect how fonts are [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlocated and instantiated during text extraction to understand the context of parser[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvocation.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fuzzer harness merely drives the text-extraction workflow; the core behavior to[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minspect resides in the PDFBox font parsing and the interaction with the fuzzing [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minstrumentation layer.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m214[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m215[0m[39m:                    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m repair Length1 and Length2 if necessary[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m216[0m[39m:                    byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m bytes = [0m[1;35mfontFile.toByteArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m217[0m[39m:                    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes.length == [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m218[0m[39m:                    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m219[0m[39m:                        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Font data unavailable"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m         [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m224[0m[39m:                    if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m & [0m[1;36m0xff[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == PFB_START_MARKER[0m[1;39m)[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m225[0m[39m:                    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m226[0m[39m:                        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m some bad files embed the entire PFB, see PDFBOX-[0m[1;36m2607[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m227[0m[39m:                        t1 = [0m[1;35mType1Font.createWithPFB[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m228[0m[39m:                    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m229[0m[39m:                    else[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m230[0m[39m:                    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m231[0m[39m:                        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m the PFB embedded as two segments back-to-back[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m232[0m[39m:                        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength1 < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || length1 > length1 + length2[0m[1;39m)[0m         [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m234[0m[39m:                            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Invalid length data, actual [0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m236[0m[39m:                        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                       [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlength1 + length2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m239[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m240[0m[39m:                        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m empty streams are simply ignored[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m241[0m[39m:                        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength1 > [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m && length2 > [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                         [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m243[0m[39m:                            t1 = [0m[1;35mType1Font.createWithSegments[0m[1;39m([0m[39msegment1, [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msegment2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Parser.jav[0m[1;92ma:541[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m553[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m541[0m[39m:    private void [0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m549[0m[39m:        else[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m550[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m551[0m[39m:            decrypted = [0m[1;35mdecrypt[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mhexToBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, EEXEC_KEY, [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m706[0m[39m:    private void [0m[1;35mreadSubrs[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint lenIV[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                        [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Parser.jav[0m[1;92ma:777[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m783[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m777[0m[39m:    private void [0m[1;35mreadCharStrings[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint lenIV[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m778[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m779[0m[39m:        int length = [0m[1;35mread[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.INTEGER[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.intValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m780[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mread[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.NAME, [0m[32m"dict"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m781[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m could actually be a sequence ending in [0m[32m"CharStrings begin"[0m[39m, too[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m782[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m instead of the [0m[32m"dup begin"[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m783[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mread[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.NAME, [0m[32m"dup"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:160[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m166[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m160[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mLOG.debug[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"record type: [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m, segment size: [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m"[0m[39m, recordType, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m161[0m[39m:            long newTotal = total + size;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m162[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnewTotal > MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m163[0m[39m:                throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"record size would be too large: "[0m[39m + [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnewTotal[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m164[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m165[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m166[0m[39m:            byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m ar = new byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[39msize[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdmodel/font/PDType1Font.jav[0m[1;92ma:223[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m229[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m223[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m224[0m[39m:                    if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m & [0m[1;36m0xff[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == PFB_START_MARKER[0m[1;39m)[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m225[0m[39m:                    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m226[0m[39m:                        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m some bad files embed the entire PFB, see PDFBOX-[0m[1;36m2607[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m227[0m[39m:                        t1 = [0m[1;35mType1Font.createWithPFB[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m228[0m[39m:                    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m229[0m[39m:                    else[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Define Resource Limits**  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. In `Type1Parser`, introduce the following `private static final` constants [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnear the top of the class:  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - `MAX_DECRYPTED_BINARY_SIZE = 20_000_000`  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - `MAX_SUBRS_COUNT = 10_000`  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - `MAX_CHARSTRINGS_COUNT = 20_000`  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. In `PfbParser`, add:  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - `MAX_PFB_SEGMENT_SIZE = 20_000_000`  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - [0m[1;39m([0m[39mOptionally tune existing `MAX_LENGTH` or keep it for overall bounding at [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m100_000_000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. In `PDType1Font` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mand/or `PDFontFactory`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, define:  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - `MAX_EMBEDDED_PFB_SIZE = 100_000_000`  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Bound Binary Decryption in Type1Parser.parseBinary**  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - At the start of `[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, before any decryption:  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes.length > MAX_DECRYPTED_BINARY_SIZE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Type1 binary segment too large [0m[32m([0m[32m"[0m[39m + bytes.length + [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m" bytes[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This prevents the fuzzer from feeding an excessively large binary payload into[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe hot parsing loop, capping the work done under instrumentation callbacks.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Cap Subroutines Count in readSubrs**  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `[0m[1;35mreadSubrs[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint lenIV[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, immediately after reading the integer count:  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     int length = [0m[1;35mread[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.INTEGER[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.intValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || length > MAX_SUBRS_COUNT[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Invalid /Subrs count: "[0m[39m + length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This stops pathological cases specifying huge counts that drive long [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdecryption loops.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Cap CharStrings Count in readCharStrings**  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `[0m[1;35mreadCharStrings[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint lenIV[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, after `int length = [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mread[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.INTEGER[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.intValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`:  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || length > MAX_CHARSTRINGS_COUNT[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Invalid /CharStrings count: "[0m[39m + length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This guards against adversarially large charstring arrays.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Limit PFB Segment Sizes in PfbParser**  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the loop inside `[0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, after decoding the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte `size`:  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39msize < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || size > MAX_PFB_SEGMENT_SIZE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"PFB segment too large: "[0m[39m + size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This stops a single PFB record from dominating parsing time. The existing [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`newTotal > MAX_LENGTH` check still applies for the sum of all segments.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Reject Oversized Embedded PFB in PDType1Font**  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `PDType1Font` constructor before invoking `[0m[1;35mType1Font.createWithPFB[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mor `[0m[1;35mType1Font.createWithSegments[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`:  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m bytes = [0m[1;35mfontFile.toByteArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes.length > MAX_EMBEDDED_PFB_SIZE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Embedded PFB font too large: "[0m[39m + bytes.length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This early check prevents downstream work on obviously excessive fonts.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. **Optionally Add Early Checks in PDFontFactory**  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `PDFontFactory.createFont`, where `new [0m[1;35mPDType1Font[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdictionary[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` is about to[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbe called, inspect `COSStream`’s `[0m[35m/[0m[95mLength[0m[39m` entries or [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mfontFile.toByteArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.length`; if it exceeds `MAX_EMBEDDED_PFB_SIZE`, throw an [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`IOException` to avoid constructing `PDType1Font` at all.[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m8[0m[39m. **Preserve Existing Behavior**  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure thresholds are high enough to accommodate real-world Type [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m fonts [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtune[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`MAX_*` constants accordingly[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The exceptions thrown are `IOException`, consistent with existing damaged-font[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhandling in `PDType1Font`, so consumers will log a warning or degrade gracefully [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithout breaking other code paths.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m9[0m[39m. **Justification and Side-Effects**  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - These size and count caps directly address unbounded loops in `Type1Parser` [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`parseBinary`, `readSubrs`, `readCharStrings`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and PFB segmentation [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`PfbParser.parsePfb`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - They throttle adversarial or malformed inputs that otherwise cause libFuzzer [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeouts via the `traceConstCmpInt` instrumentation callback.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Legitimate fonts—typically well under these thresholds—will continue to parse [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnormally. If extremely large but valid fonts exist, thresholds can be raised or [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmade configurable via system properties.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No changes are made to harness, fuzzing logic, external dependencies, or test [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode, preserving existing tests and fuzzer integration.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m10[0m[39m. **References in Codebase**  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    - The approach mirrors the existing `MAX_LENGTH` check in `PfbParser`, [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mextending it to per-segment and binary parse boundaries.  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    - The `DamagedFontException`[0m[35m/[0m[39m`IOException` handling in `PDType1Font` already [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39misolates parser failures, so our new checks integrate seamlessly into the [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39merror-handling flows.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBy implementing these guarded thresholds at appropriate parser entry points, we [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontain worst-case parsing time and prevent libFuzzer timeouts without altering [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnormal functionality.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJNI global refs: [0m[1;36m26[0m[39m, weak refs: [0m[1;36m0[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue is a libFuzzer timeout during fuzz testing of PDF text [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mextraction. The JVM thread dump shows the “main” thread stuck in [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Type1Parser.parseBinary`, deep in font parsing and decryption callbacks.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch attempt adds size and count limits in the FontBox `Type1Parser` and in [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPDFBox’s `PDType1Font` constructor:  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- A maximum decrypted binary size  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Maximum `[0m[35m/[0m[95mSubrs[0m[39m` and `[0m[35m/[0m[95mCharStrings[0m[39m` counts  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- A maximum PFB font size  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter applying these checks, libFuzzer still reports a timeout with no change in [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbehavior.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fuzzer harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`PDFExtractTextFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m repeatedly [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvokes PDFBox’s text extraction on arbitrary input.  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - During these runs, libFuzzer reports a timeout rather than a crash, indicating[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat some inputs cause excessively long execution.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Thread dump shows the “main” thread in a RUNNABLE state inside [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Type1Parser.parseBinary`, specifically in a native callback [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`TraceDataFlowNativeCallbacks.traceConstCmpInt`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and then proceeding through [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mencryption/decryption and font parsing [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`Type1Parser`, `Type1Font`, `PDType1Font`, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PDFTextStripper`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Important Observations  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - parseBinary is processing a potentially very large or maliciously crafted byte[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39marray.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No exception or crash is raised; execution simply does not complete in time.  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The stack trace traverses both FontBox [0m[1;39m([0m[39mType1 parsing[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and PDFBox [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfont [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfactory and text stripper[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m code paths, suggesting the timeout arises from the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing logic.  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `org.apache.fontbox.type1.Type1Parser`:  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Added `MAX_DECRYPTED_BINARY_SIZE = 20_000_000` and an early `IOException` if[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe binary segment is too large.  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Added `MAX_SUBRS_COUNT = 10_000` with bounds checks around `[0m[35m/[0m[95mSubrs[0m[39m` array [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocation.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Added `MAX_CHARSTRINGS_COUNT = 20_000` with bounds checks around [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[35m/[0m[95mCharStrings[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `org.apache.pdfbox.pdmodel.font.PDType1Font`:  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Added an upper limit of 100_000_000 bytes on embedded PFB data, throwing [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`IOException` if exceeded.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - After recompiling with these changes and rerunning the fuzzer, the result [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremains `ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout`. No new exceptions or crashes are observed.  [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Areas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The decryption loop and hex-to-binary conversion in `Type1Parser.parseBinary`,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto identify unexpected large allocations or nested loops.  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The `repairLength1` [0m[35m/[0m[39m `repairLength2` routines in `PDType1Font`, which adjust [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moffsets and may loop over the byte array.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The lexer/parser state machine in `Type1Parser` around large or malformed [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcharstring dictionaries.  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Potential performance hotspots in PDFTextStripper’s content stream processing,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mespecially font switching [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`SetFontAndSize`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Interaction between the native tracing callbacks and the Java-side decryption [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlogic, which may contribute to slowdown.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNo causal conclusions or further mitigation steps are offered here; this report [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfocuses on documenting the observed behavior, the attempted size checks, and [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlisting the code areas that warrant deeper profiling and analysis.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHere is the initial issue log of the codebase:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<issue>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2025[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m12[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m27[0m[39m [0m[1;92m17:01:59[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mFull thread dump OpenJDK [0m[1;36m64[0m[39m-Bit Server VM [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m17.0[0m[39m.[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m+[0m[1;36m8[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m86[0m[39m mixed mode, sharing[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m        [2m                [0m
